{
 "name": "RPlog_Trouble_on_Cloud_City_Part_Two_--_Malign_s_Court",
 "title": "Trouble on Cloud City, Part Two: Malign's Court",
 "summary": "The Sith Imperator Malign descends on Bespin with an overwhelming fleet, his Circle of Irluuk acolytes, and his sister Johanna -- now Grand Moff of the sector -- to root out a 'pest problem' and hold court. The Jedi Jessalyn and her companion Basca Starker, attempting to flee, are intercepted and compelled to attend a tense dinner where old wounds, accusations, and political revelations spill across the table: the Caspian Presav Crestian Tarasar reports rescuing Force-sensitive younglings from Trandoshan raiders, Basca exposes himself as an Imperium agent, and Johanna confronts the darkness Vadim planted within Basca. As Johanna and Jessalyn probe the Sith spawn 'Stayn' through the Force, the immortal Vadim manifests through him, the Circle's monstrous director Sigil Rexton and the mutant Wookiee honor guard close in, and Crestian draws a blaster. Johanna asserts her legal authority over her own world to spare Basca's life for the moment, Malign acquiescing, and an uneasy, violence-charged truce settles over the court even as Crestian, Tracer, and Kipran vow not to forget the night's treacheries.",
